OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FMore money to cut NHS waiting times
OL,7,Fhere in Wales is likely to be at the
OL,8,Ftop of Welsh Government spending plans
OL,9,Ffor the coming financial year.
OL,11,FThe Finance Secretary Mark Drakeford
OL,12,Fwill set out the Labour government's
OL,13,FDraft Budget for 2025-6 in the Senedd
OL,14,Fon Tuesday 10 December, with a bigger
OL,15,Fpot of money available than ever
OL,16,Fbefore.
