OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FIn the UK Government's recent budget,
OL,7,Fthe Chancellor said there would be an
OL,8,Fextra #1.7bn for the Welsh Government.
OL,9,FSome of that was for the current
OL,10,Ffinancial year, but Mr Drakeford will
OL,11,Fhave at least an extra #1bn to spend,
OL,12,Fbringing the total Welsh Government
OL,13,Fbudget to around #24bn.
OL,15,FThose who run public services hope
OL,16,Fit'll mean a reversal of the tight
OL,17,Fbudgets and cuts of recent years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
