OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FBut rising costs and pay rises will
OL,7,Feat into much of the new money and the
OL,8,Fplans may run into political trouble:
OL,9,FLabour doesn't have a majority of
OL,10,Fvotes in the Senedd and opposition
OL,11,Fparties may be unwilling to reach a
OL,12,Fdeal to help the budget pass.
OL,14,FSince becoming First Minister, Eluned
OL,15,FMorgan has repeatedly said that she is
OL,16,Ffocussing on four priorities and those
OL,17,Fareas will almost certainly see the
OL,18,Fbulk of any new spending increases.
