OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FShe says she wants to cut waiting
OL,7,Ftimes in the NHS, create 'green jobs',
OL,8,Fboost standards in schools and
OL,9,Fcolleges, provide more low-rent homes
OL,10,Fand transform transport links here in
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FYou can expect spending decisions to
OL,14,Fbe in those areas, particularly more
OL,15,Fmoney for the NHS and schools but
OL,16,Fthere are other demands.
OL,18,FBusiness rates relief?
