OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FWill the Finance Secretary choose to
OL,7,Fmeet concerns from businesses in the
OL,8,Fretail, hospitality and leisure
OL,9,Fsectors about the business rates
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FIt's the Welsh Government's
OL,13,Fresponsibility here in Wales where
OL,14,Fbusiness rates are known as 'non-
OL,15,Fdomestic rates.'
OL,17,FFor the current financial year
OL,18,Fbusinesses in the retail, hospitality
OL,19,Fand leisure sectors have been able to
OL,20,Fclaim 40% relief, a reduction from the
OL,21,Fcovid-era 75%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
