OL,6,FTheir counterparts in England have
OL,7,Fcontinued to enjoy 75% relief although
OL,8,Fthe Chancellor Rachel Reeves announced
OL,9,Fthat that would be reduced to 40% from
OL,10,FApril 2025.
OL,12,FOrganisations such as the Federation
OL,13,Fof Small Businesses and the trade body
OL,14,FUK Hospitality Cymru have urged the
OL,15,FWelsh Government to extend business
OL,16,Frate relief in the Draft Budget and
OL,17,Fkeep the level at least at 40%.
