OL,6,FWelsh Labour's conference in Llandudno
OL,7,Fin November saw a large number of
OL,8,Ffarmers park their tractors on the
OL,9,Fprom to protest outside Venue Cymru.
OL,11,FTheir main concern was about changes
OL,12,Fto Inheritance Tax announced by the
OL,13,FChancellor, which is something out of
OL,14,Fthe control of Eluned Morgan's Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment.
