OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FBut previous protests at the
OL,7,Fconference and in Cardiff Bay were
OL,8,Fdirected at Labour's proposed
OL,9,FSustainable Farming Scheme,
OL,10,Fparticularly a requirement to devote
OL,11,F10% of agricultural land to tree cover
OL,12,Fin order to qualify for payments.
OL,14,FThe farming unions, NFU Cymru and the
OL,15,FFUW, both say they wants the current
OL,16,FBasic Payment Scheme to be kept at the
OL,17,Fsame level for the coming financial
OL,18,Fyear and for the rural affairs budget
OL,19,Fto be restored to the level it was at
OL,20,Fbefore it was cut by 13% in 2023.
