OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FThe impact of Storm Bert in November
OL,7,Fbrought renewed focus to the need for
OL,8,Fadequate flood defences and warning
OL,9,Fsystems.
OL,11,FIn the wake of the most recent
OL,12,Fflooding, Eluned Morgan has
OL,13,Fhighlighted the #300m that she says
OL,14,Fhas been spent on flood defences since
OL,15,F2020, meaning that hundreds rather
OL,16,Fthan thousands of homes and businesses
OL,17,Fwere flooded this time around.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/15
