OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FBut she acknowledged that more needs
OL,7,Fto be done and the draft budget could
OL,8,Fprove the opportunity to announce more
OL,9,Ffunding for defences.
OL,11,FThere will be an expectation too of
OL,12,Ffunding for coal tip safety, after the
OL,13,Fannouncement of #25m from the UK
OL,14,FGovernment and action in the form of a
OL,15,FCoal Tip Safety Bill unveiled this
OL,16,Fweek.
OL,18,FBut the total cost is estimated at
OL,19,F#600m over 10-15 years. Campaigners
OL,20,Fwill be looking for details in the
OL,21,Fdraft budget.
