OL,6,FPolitical problems
OL,8,FThe Welsh Government will publish its
OL,9,FDraft Budget today (Tuesday 10th
OL,10,FDecember) and it will be debated in
OL,11,Fthe Senedd chamber.
OL,13,FThere won't be a vote at this stage.
OL,14,FInstead the proposals are scrutinised
OL,15,Fby the different Senedd committees.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/15
