OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FThere'll be another debate in the
OL,7,Fchamber at the beginning of February;
OL,8,Fthe Final Budget will be published at
OL,9,Fthe end of February and the plans will
OL,10,Fbe debated and voted on by MSs on the
OL,11,F4th March.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government needs a majority
OL,14,Fof votes in the Senedd to pass its
OL,15,Fbudget but it only has exactly half
OL,16,Fthe seats. It needs at least one other
OL,17,FMS to vote for it or abstain.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/15
