OL,3,CCutting NHS waiting times likely to
OL,4,Ctop Welsh spending plans in Budget
OL,6,FIf the process reaches this point, the
OL,7,FSenedd will be in a period of
OL,8,Fpolitical crisis. Failure to pass a
OL,9,Fbudget is usually seen as failure of a
OL,10,Fgovernment to gain the confidence of a
OL,11,Fparliament and could well force Eluned
OL,12,FMorgan to resign.
OL,14,FAll of which explains why she is
OL,15,Flooking to reach a deal with another
OL,16,Fparty or parties. The lone Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrat MS is one target; Plaid Cymru
OL,18,Fis another.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/15
