OL,6,FThe Conservatives are unlikely to
OL,7,Freach a deal with Labour but the other
OL,8,Ftwo parties will be holding out for a
OL,9,Fsignificant concession. They've both
OL,10,Fbeen publicly very critical of the
OL,11,FLabour Welsh Government and it's not
OL,12,Fyet clear if either will be won over.
